parameters: It will be 10G per night. Will you be staying over?
Whenever I see an inn's bed, I just want to jump on it.

Have you forgotten how you broke the bed by jumping on it
too hard and got scolded...?
Ahaha... I guess something like that did happen...

The treasure chest over there contains the money for my
grandma's medical treatment. After years of saving, I can
finally take her to the hospital!

Um, Memerisu-chan... you're not thinking of anything weird,
are you...?
Sorry... Grandma. It's because I'm weak...
Let's give the money back! This is just too cruel-!!

If you want to get your money back, you better get
stronger... guheheheheheh!!!

I can't believe I lost... Take it, thief. I'll just have to
save up for grandma's treatment again.

If you need money, why not come to Chern village? There
might be some work for you there.

You've got some nerve talking about money after stealing it!
But I can't choose when it comes to my grandma's sake...
I'll head to that village!
The innkeeper's grandson has joined your party!
Are you really going to open it?
I'm sorry... Grandma. It's because I'm weak...
You thieving bastard! Get out of here now!
This smells dangerous... Let's stop here.
